华开展对话的邀请，也欢迎巴以双方谈判代表在华举行直接谈判。 王毅最后表示，联合国和安理会能否有所作为，世界人民在看，历史也在记录。我们应该也必须团结一致，站在和平正义一边，站在公道良知一边，站在历史正确一边，践行真正的多边主义，推动巴勒斯坦问题早日得到全面、公正、持久的解决。 与会代表感谢中方主持召开此次紧急公开会，普遍呼吁以巴双方立即停火止暴，遵守有关安理会决议和国际法，推动局势降温。各方认为安理会成员和国际社会应发出一致声音，公正推进巴以和谈进程，努力推动巴以两国实现和平共处。 来源：外交部"},"attached_info":"Cj8I39zW5MjL9MdjEAMaCDY0NDUzMDkwIK7yg4UGMDo42xFAC3IJNDU5Nzc4ODQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"153 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-42954d1db8b7bc10b97c06dc557f6d98_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1621297594.4598022","card_id":"Q_309398217","target":{"id":309398217,"title":"哪些情侣一看就能在一起很久很久?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/309398217","type":"question","created":1547700307,"answer_count":951,"follower_count":13092,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4728,4729,11604],"comment_count":44,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"1. 会吵架，但不会冷战 2. 三观相同，相互理解彼此 3. 女生不作，男生不浪 4. 一定要相互付出 5. 男生会秀恩爱 6. 可能不经常在朋友圈秀恩爱 7. 一个宠，一个崇拜 8. 有很多恩爱的细节 9. 护短 10. 两个人都觉得对方是丑的"},"attached_info":"Cj8I39zW5MjL9MdjEAMaCDMxMDMxOTc1INOQgOIFMCw4pGZADHIJMzA5Mzk4MjE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"151 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-b103838a5c2232b3e2510c9d33d8cdd8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1621297594.4604528","card_id":"Q_458085883","target":{"id":458085883,"title":"当欠债金额达到一辈子也还不了的情况，你会怎么办？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/458085883","type":"question","created":1620297334,"answer_count":75,"follower_count":154,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[11432,33553,48112],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,